window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>In the electrifying new series <i>The Hive: A Thriller</i>, CIA cyber-ops officer Samantha Sloane stumbles onto a mystery that leads straight into her own forgotten past. Her search for answers draws her into the orbit of Eli Cooper, the elusive CEO of a billion-dollar cybersecurity firm and his group of elite hackers who make up The Hive. But the more Sam learns about Eli and his company, the more she realizes she can't trust anyone around her.</p> <p>Starring Tony Hale, Taylor Dearden, Brandon Routh, Samira Wiley, and Margo Martindale, the series follows Sam as she’s trapped between the agency that raised her and the rogue survivors it left behind.</p> <p>Executive Produced by Tony Hale, the Hive is a gripping story of psychological warfare, digital espionage, and what it means to own your past.</p> <p>Available in Dolby Atmos on Audible.</p>"; 
